                    </div>
                </div>
                <img alt="Canadian Maple Leaf" class="home-blog-icon" src="/images/maple-leaf.svg">
            </div>
            {# GC Jobs Banner =============================================== #}
            <div class="gradient-right-left" data-c-padding="normal">
                <div data-c-alignment="center" data-c-container="layout">
                    <p data-c-colour="white" data-c-margin="top(half) bottom(half)">Can't find the job you're looking for on Talent Cloud?
